name: Pending
definition: Not yet decided or settled; awaiting conclusion or confirmation.

name: Running
definition: A running state is a state during which a device or service performs its specified function in normal operation.

name: Success
definition: An event that accomplishes its intended purpose.

name: Failed
definition: Having undergone failure; did not accomplish the intended purpose.

name: Canceled
definition: Postpone indefinitely or annul something that was scheduled.
